{"type": "article", "id": 60863, "title": "这款新式陀螺，玩的是视错觉游戏｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-01-31T23:06:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 8503, "name": "雪弗兰"}, {"id": 929, "name": "乐高"}, {"id": 56398, "name": "Colony"}, {"id": 56399, "name": "emnos"}, {"id": 56400, "name": "Dims"}, {"id": 56401, "name": "M-S-D-S Studio"}, {"id": 56402, "name": "+d"}, {"id": 56403, "name": "Yuichi Nara"}, {"id": 56404, "name": "Jordi Lopez Aguilo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 121, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190201000232ldeko6gCqymVAUKZ.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: #101010} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: #101010} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: #101010; min-height: 13.0px} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 20.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626; background-color: #ffffff; min-height: 22.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #101010} span.s6 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Sp!n by  Jordi Lopez Aguilo</h3><p>日本设计品牌 + d 推出了一个新款陀螺，名为 Sp!n。当你旋转它时，悬浮的视错觉会创造出意想不到的效果，除了陀螺本身的游戏乐趣，视觉上令人惊叹的效果也是其亮点之一。</p><p>Sp!n 出自设计师 Jordi Lopez Aguilo 之手，它既可以正面朝上也可以倒置。如果发力方式正确的话，它可以旋转大约 1 分钟左右。目前，Sp!n有 5 种不同颜色，零售价为 972 日元，<a href=\"https://koncent.jp/?pid=136109442\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201000317BaYK0fGL21rzscFp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201000317WmBKkSLi0gnX9feU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667408\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201000336kERtBobcn9MLiXFp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Eave Table by M-S-D-S Studio for Dims</h3><p>多伦多设计工作室 M-S-D-S Studio 最近为家具品牌 Dims 设计了一款名为 Eave 的极简主义餐桌。这款多用途餐桌专为小空间而设计，简洁的线条，柔和的曲线和一些醒目的细节，将其和商务风格的办公桌区别开来。</p><p>Dims 希望创造一个平板包装方式的桌子，桌腿部分由 FSC 认证的实心灰木制成，桌面由蜂窝芯和灰板制成。目前，Eave 餐桌有两种颜色：天然灰和薄荷灰，它采用彩色磁性配件，可牢固地卡在连接硬件上，添入了意想不到的色彩和独特的设计细节。售价 476 美元，<a href=\"https://www.dimshome.com/products/eave-table\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001017Tl4Wb3UAhy20JLS6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667200\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001017Ec3DBSOxMFa5h9dn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902010010172INVCcEBUz9DinZX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902010010189Cq8h51ZEncFsNj6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902010010185B92dsrOmbgNMuY0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001018J3ekZQPCmRMTX9iW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001018ru09DMI5cXnxRaz6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.161600\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mono Wall Clock by Yuichi Nara </h3><p>日本设计师 Yuichi Nara 为钟表制造商 Lemnos 设计了一款名为 Mono 的挂钟，造型简约却引人注目。它采用清晰的黑白配色，就像是钢琴般的琴键设计。</p><p>Mono 的框架由铝铸件制成，是在富山县高冈市的铸造生产中心制作出来的。Lemnos 一直以其完全静音的挂钟而闻名，Mono Clock 也不例外。这款时钟的低调设计，意味着它可以丰富任何现代室内空间，引人注目却又不显得突兀。售价 150 美元，<a href=\"https://www.odetothings.com/collections/all/products/mono-clock?variant=18716633727049\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902010010493GcPQlO25xDqnAf1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001049RO3g8u2rmJByoUwq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001049mp8yIdATWfRYk4ig.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001050kqpUNzjBreLP6XKy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001050lsUxwb3zYtdLqcSH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001050san3pmfebl0tHBKW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Conception Series by Molly Haynes for Colony</h3><p>全球设计与战略公司 Colony 推出 The Conception 系列新品，团队希望能够挖掘新兴美国设计人才、艺术家和工匠。</p><p>The Conception 系列亮相的第一个创意人是 Molly Haynes，她是一位来自纽约的编织手工艺人，专注于尝试创造性技术和尊重天然材料。Molly Haynes 的作品，集中体现了大自然的质感，试图将每件作品转变为自己制作的一处景观。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001112PDuhI5EcYXdwTZVk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001112AnjMpILQfJuHCehs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.465432\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001113bPx7BvrLtMqFSj2p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.628906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001113ZQwfm5gD2nBypohN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001113scVloyfdamZAG7v6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902010011136f3jNSgBrqLVKIwi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902010011148fFGYI1O9AXyMsDT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://goodcolony.com/the-conception-series/\" rel=\"nofollow\">goodcolony</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>2019 Silverado 1500 LT Trail Boss pickup truck</h3><p>这辆雪弗兰西尔维拉多由 18 位乐高迷花费 2000 小时和 334544 块乐高积木搭建而成。</p><p>这是一辆全尺寸 2019 款西尔维拉多 1500LT 型卡车的复制品，由雪弗兰和乐高合作出品。</p><p>参与制作的是在牛津社区学校举办的第一届乐高联赛中的学生，和乐高在底特律启动的一个创新项目中的乐高拼装专家们共同完成，根据软件制作好的方案，经过不断调试，一块块拼起来的。</p><p>雪弗兰出品的西尔维拉多是美国著名的卡车品牌，一辆真正的西尔维拉多可运载6700 磅，但这个玩具版的西尔维拉多的承重能力仍然可以到令人惊讶的 3307 磅。毕竟，这个乐高玩具有 6 英尺高，20 英尺长和 8 英尺宽，并装有可工作的前车灯。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001156wsFMCjxRoAPld7bz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690625\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001156UQ0tH7ErRNqV4Zuo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.492188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001156V9Kp1i8SG3eHvsqA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.711719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001157oENnRZMIXGfwL7Jg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001157Wt7H0hbxC5eZ1cOK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001158TOWtPamJdVuvCFyL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.567187\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190201001157FjpMzykrsovWCVYt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.689063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: #101010} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: #101010} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} </style>"}